= General Information
HabuL is an improved fork of Habu, original addon by Will Harris.

The addon is lightweight and has a single basic feature, that is
to select all junk mail in the current folder and send it to
specified recipients.

= Setup

Select Tools -> Addons and configure HabuL preferences. You can turn on/off
options related to various spam reporting services.

= Usage

Add the "Report" button to your toolbar and click it to send a spam report
containing all emails marked as "junk" which are present in the current
directory.

Please note that after successful sending all junk emails in the current
directory will be deleted, moved to trash or left untouched.
